some dame.

346
00:21:22,709 --> 00:21:24,750
Don't call her that.

347
00:21:24,792 --> 00:21:26,041
You'll see.

348
00:21:26,083 --> 00:21:28,667
You'll see how tough
Mickey D is.

349
00:21:28,709 --> 00:21:30,417
He's nothing.

350
00:21:32,458 --> 00:21:34,375
(<i> deep sigh</i> )

351
00:21:35,709 --> 00:21:37,041
I want some answers.

352
00:21:37,083 --> 00:21:38,375
I'm sure the concierge
