361
00:22:01,041 --> 00:22:03,083
PICARD:
Riker, can you read me?

362
00:22:03,125 --> 00:22:04,500
Yes.

363
00:22:04,542 --> 00:22:06,583
There's a good deal of
interference, Captain,

364
00:22:06,625 --> 00:22:08,375
but you are getting through.

365
00:22:09,959 --> 00:22:12,166
Number One, why haven't
you left that building?

366
00:22:12,208 --> 00:22:15,041
We tried, sir, it seems
like we're trapped in here.

367
00:22:15,083 --> 00:22:17,917
We're in no immediate danger,
but I am concerned.

368
00:22:17,959 --> 00:22:21,250
Something about your location is
interfering with communication.

369
00:22:21,291 --> 00:22:22,875
We are working on the problem.

370
00:22:22,917 --> 00:22:24,542
RIKER:
Standing by, sir.

371
00:22:24,583 --> 00:22:26,333
Captain, these frequencies
are unstable.

372
00:22:26,375 --> 00:22:27,458
Then find others.

373
00:22:27,500 --> 00:22:28,792
Yes, sir.

374
00:22:32,333 --> 00:22:34,917
What is going on
down there?

375
00:22:41,375 --> 00:22:43,083
DATA:
Commander?

376
00:22:44,500 --> 00:22:46,208
I am picking up
something most unusual

377
00:22:46,250 --> 00:22:48,709
in another section
of this structure.

378
00:22:48,750 --> 00:22:50,458
It appears to be human DNA.

379
00:22:50,500 --> 00:22:51,750
Where?

380
00:22:51,792 --> 00:22:55,083
31.9 meters above
and to the right of us.

381
00:22:56,542 --> 00:22:59,333
Perhaps those turbolifts
could take us there.

382
00:23:06,125 --> 00:23:08,542
Seems to be
malfunctioning.

383
00:23:10,792 --> 00:23:12,667
(<i> elevator dings</i> )

384
00:23:21,875 --> 00:23:23,542
(<i> elevator dings</i> )

385
00:23:32,208 --> 00:23:35,625
The reading I received is
from behind this door, sir.

386
00:23:54,709 --> 00:23:57,125
My reading is
intensifying, sir.

387
00:23:58,500 --> 00:24:00,208
RIKER:
Are you getting any life signs?

388
00:24:00,250 --> 00:24:02,083
None, sir.

389
00:24:18,291 --> 00:24:21,250
Definitely human.
Male.

390
00:24:21,291 --> 00:24:24,083
Looks like the poor devil
died in his sleep.

391
00:24:25,625 --> 00:24:29,333
What a terrible
way to die.

392
00:24:29,375 --> 00:24:32,458
