00:24:42,625 --> 00:24:44,333
WORF:
Commander.

398
00:24:46,875 --> 00:24:49,041
Is this significant, sir?

399
00:24:51,125 --> 00:24:53,417
American.

400
00:24:53,458 --> 00:24:54,917
DATA:
52 stars, sir.

401
00:24:54,959 --> 00:24:59,000
Places it between
2033 and 2079 A.D.

402
00:24:59,041 --> 00:25:01,583
Correlates with the
debris we found.

403
00:25:06,250 --> 00:25:08,667
Colonel S. Richey.

404
00:25:10,959 --> 00:25:13,542
Rest in peace,
Colonel.

405
00:25:16,083 --> 00:25:17,959
Picard to Riker.

406
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:20,500
Finally.
Riker. Go ahead.

407
00:25:20,542 --> 00:25:22,166
You're coming through
clearly now.

408
00:25:22,208 --> 00:25:24,083
What's your situation?

409
00:25:24,125 --> 00:25:26,166
Well, this structure was
apparently made to resemble

410
00:25:26,208 --> 00:25:27,792
20th century Earth.

411
00:25:27,834 --> 00:25:29,625
All attempts to exit
have failed.

412
00:25:29,667 --> 00:25:32,125
PICARD: We haven't found a way
to transport you back yet.

413
00:25:32,166 --> 00:25:33,500
I assumed as much, sir.

414
00:25:33,542 --> 00:25:35,458
We've also located the
remains of a human.

415
00:25:35,500 --> 00:25:37,667
Request
identity scan.

416
00:25:37,709 --> 00:25:40,000
Colonel Richey,
American,

417
00:25:40,041 --> 00:25:41,083
first initial, "S."

418
00:25:41,125 --> 00:25:42,834
Roughly the same
time period.

419
00:25:42,875 --> 00:25:44,542
Do it.

420
00:25:45,917 --> 00:25:49,417
Commander,
some curiosities.

421
00:25:51,625 --> 00:25:55,792
Books.
A novel--<i> Hotel Royale.</i>

