00:25:55,834 --> 00:25:57,792
Summarize, please.

423
00:26:01,083 --> 00:26:03,166
Information retrieved,
Captain.

424
00:26:04,166 --> 00:26:05,417
Number One?

425
00:26:05,458 --> 00:26:06,667
RIKER:
Go ahead, Captain.

426
00:26:06,709 --> 00:26:08,834
We have the information
you requested.

427
00:26:08,875 --> 00:26:12,125
Colonel Stephen Richey
was the commanding officer

428
00:26:12,166 --> 00:26:13,917
of the explorer ship
<i>Charybdis,</i>

429
00:26:13,959 --> 00:26:19,375
