launch date of July 23, 2037.

430
00:26:19,417 --> 00:26:21,250
It was the third
manned attempt

431
00:26:21,291 --> 00:26:24,375
to travel beyond the confines
of Earth's solar system.

432
00:26:24,417 --> 00:26:28,959
Its telemetry failed,
it was never heard from again.

433
00:26:29,000 --> 00:26:31,166
Do you believe that
you've discovered

434
00:26:31,208 --> 00:26:33,000
the remains of
Colonel Richey?

435
00:26:33,041 --> 00:26:34,625
Yes. And Captain,
we found something else.

436
00:26:34,667 --> 00:26:38,500
A novel by Todd Matthews
entitled<i> Hotel Royale,</i>

437
00:26:38,542 --> 00:26:39,959
which is the name
of this structure.

438
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:41,625
Data.

439
00:26:41,667 --> 00:26:45,291
Captain, this is the story of
a group of compulsive gamblers

440
00:26:45,333 --> 00:26:48,000
