corruption and deceit.

441
00:26:48,041 --> 00:26:51,125
It is told by
nefarious lothario, Mickey D,

442
00:26:51,166 --> 00:26:53,500
who appears only at the
climax of the story,

443
00:26:53,542 --> 00:26:55,375
to carry out the
cold-blooded murder

444
00:26:55,417 --> 00:26:56,917
of the hotel bellboy.

445
00:26:56,959 --> 00:26:59,583
There is also a subplot
about an older man

446
00:26:59,625 --> 00:27:01,208
