instantaneous.

490
00:29:03,667 --> 00:29:05,583
RIKER: But I assume
you could revive us?

491
00:29:05,625 --> 00:29:08,417
Yes, in theory.

492
00:29:08,458 --> 00:29:10,417
PICARD:
You must understand, Number One.

493
00:29:10,458 --> 00:29:12,792
We'll wait here for
months if necessary.

494
00:29:12,834 --> 00:29:15,333
We're just
considering options.

495
00:29:15,375 --> 00:29:16,834
RIKER:
If you're trying to motivate us

496
00:29:16,875 --> 00:29:18,542
