507
00:30:10,083 --> 00:30:11,834
We'll go to explore
the rest of the hotel.

508
00:30:11,875 --> 00:30:13,750
We'll keep a com line open.
You two, go down

509
00:30:13,792 --> 00:30:15,291
to the lobby and see if there's
anything that we missed.

510
00:30:15,333 --> 00:30:16,709
You talk to the guests,
try to find out

511
00:30:16,750 --> 00:30:18,000
who or what they are.

