528
00:31:38,583 --> 00:31:41,542
Damn!
Oh, shoot!

529
00:31:41,583 --> 00:31:43,500
How much do I
have left here?

530
00:31:43,542 --> 00:31:45,125
Honey, now, you know
it's bad luck

