chips at the table.

532
00:31:46,750 --> 00:31:48,583
Yeah?
Excuse me, sir.

533
00:31:48,625 --> 00:31:52,000
Might I inquire,
where are you from?

534
00:31:52,041 --> 00:31:54,208
Lubbock, Texas.

535
00:31:54,250 --> 00:31:56,750
And how did
you get here?

536
00:31:56,792 --> 00:31:57,917
To Vegas?

537
00:31:57,959 --> 00:31:59,333
Drove my car.

538
00:31:59,375 --> 00:32:02,417
I got a '91 Caddy with
only 80,000 miles on it.

539
00:32:02,458 --> 00:32:04,000
Where is your
automobile now?

540
00:32:04,041 --> 00:32:05,709
Out front, I suppose.

541
00:32:05,750 --> 00:32:07,625
What the hell difference
does it make?

542
00:32:07,667 --> 00:32:09,792
Could you take me there?

543
00:32:09,834 --> 00:32:11,458
WOMAN:
Hit me.

544
00:32:12,625 --> 00:32:14,583
I'm losing my shirt.

545
00:32:15,875 --> 00:32:18,250
TEXAS: Son, why would
I want to do that?

546
00:32:18,291 --> 00:32:21,166
Can't you see I'm trying
to help this little lady?

547
00:32:21,208 --> 00:32:24,667
