inside the Royale,

548
00:32:24,709 --> 00:32:26,542
just as I am.

549
00:32:26,583 --> 00:32:29,041
Sure does seem that way when
you're losing, don't it?

550
00:32:29,083 --> 00:32:31,542
We're just trying to
turn this lady wagon around

551
00:32:31,583 --> 00:32:33,542
and win back some
lost change.

552
00:32:33,583 --> 00:32:35,583
Otherwise, she's in
a desperate situation

553
00:32:35,625 --> 00:32:37,583
and she's got nowhere to turn.

554
00:32:37,625 --> 00:32:39,041
Well...

555
