581
00:34:16,041 --> 00:34:18,333
Why don't you just
take this outside?

582
00:34:18,375 --> 00:34:19,583
Yeah.

583
00:34:19,625 --> 00:34:21,083
I like that.

584
00:34:21,125 --> 00:34:23,208
Come on, baggage man.

585
00:34:23,250 --> 00:34:26,208
