take it outside.

586
00:34:26,250 --> 00:34:28,959
BELLBOY: When I was a kid,
I used to look up to you guys.

587
00:34:29,000 --> 00:34:32,583
The suit,
the fancy shoes.

588
00:34:32,625 --> 00:34:35,583
I really thought that
made you somebody.

589
00:34:35,625 --> 00:34:37,458
But you're nobody.

590
00:34:37,500 --> 00:34:39,250
(<i> Picard lowers volume</i> )

591
