this dialogue.

592
00:34:41,125 --> 00:34:43,500
Did humans really
talk like that?

593
00:34:43,542 --> 00:34:45,125
Not in real life.

594
00:34:45,166 --> 00:34:47,750
Remember, everything that's
going on down there

