629
00:37:09,250 --> 00:37:13,667
They return home, leaving the
assistant manager in charge.

630
00:37:17,375 --> 00:37:22,250
Captain, that's how
we're getting out.

631
00:37:24,250 --> 00:37:26,709
We're buying this place.

632
00:37:34,083 --> 00:37:36,333
It is all a question
of probabilities.

633
00:37:36,375 --> 00:37:37,625
Quite simple, really,

