a place to sleep.

651
00:38:19,959 --> 00:38:22,041
Don't you worry your
little head, honey.

652
00:38:22,083 --> 00:38:24,250
I'd never let that happen.

653
00:38:29,709 --> 00:38:31,166
Go, baby.
Let's go.

654
00:38:31,208 --> 00:38:32,500
Here they come.
Here they come, babe.

655
00:38:32,542 --> 00:38:34,500
CROUPIER: Seven, out.
TEXAS: Ah, I'm out.

656
00:38:36,500 --> 00:38:37,917
Your turn, slick.

657
00:38:37,959 --> 00:38:39,250
Go to work.

658
00:38:39,291 --> 00:38:41,917
Maybe this turkey will
bring us some luck.

659
00:38:52,709 --> 00:38:54,917
Six.
Six is your number.

660
00:38:54,959 --> 00:38:57,291
Hell, my blind grandma
can make a six, boy.

661
00:38:57,333 --> 00:38:58,875
Come on, roll 'em.

662
00:38:58,917 --> 00:39:01,250
I thought seven
and 11 had value.

663
00:39:01,291 --> 00:39:03,250
Actually, six is a valid point.

664
00:39:03,291 --> 00:39:05,125
Of course, now, the objective
is to roll

665
00:39:05,166 --> 00:39:07,333
