random fortune involved.

669
00:39:14,667 --> 00:39:17,083
I believe that is why
they call it gambling.

670
00:39:17,125 --> 00:39:19,125
Yeah.

671
00:39:23,208 --> 00:39:25,792
CROUPIER: Seven.
Seven away. Next shooter.

672
00:39:25,834 --> 00:39:28,041
So much for
your new turkey.

673
00:39:28,083 --> 00:39:30,000
Give slick another shot.

674
00:39:30,041 --> 00:39:32,417
I got a feeling
about you, boy.

675
00:39:36,208 --> 00:39:39,542
