improperly balanced.

676
00:39:39,583 --> 00:39:41,375
I believe their final
resting position would be--

677
00:39:41,417 --> 00:39:42,834
Can you repair them?

678
00:39:44,000 --> 00:39:45,250
I believe so.

679
00:39:47,625 --> 00:39:49,542
I will make another attempt.

680
00:39:53,000 --> 00:39:55,375
Baby needs a new pair
of shoes.

681
00:39:57,959 --> 00:39:59,709
11! That a boy.

682
00:39:59,750 --> 00:40:02,667
Do that a few more times,
we all gonna get well.

683
00:40:04,750 --> 00:40:06,917
Whoo!

684
00:40:06,959 --> 00:40:08,500
Seven, winner.

685
00:40:08,542 --> 00:40:11,792
And another one!
(<i> laughing</i> )

686
00:40:11,834 --> 00:40:14,166
Keep going, boy, we got 'em
hot now, let's go, let's go!

687
00:40:14,208 --> 00:40:15,709
RIKER: Double 'em up.
Here we go.

688
00:40:15,750 --> 00:40:17,875
Keep it rolling, boy,
keep it rolling.

689
00:40:19,583 --> 00:40:21,959
