00:41:04,875 --> 00:41:07,291
Yes, sir.
12.3 million.

706
00:41:07,333 --> 00:41:09,125
Perhaps I
will bet...

707
00:41:09,166 --> 00:41:10,834
$700,000.

708
00:41:10,875 --> 00:41:13,041
No, bet it all.

709
00:41:13,083 --> 00:41:16,333
But sir, the sale price of this
edifice is 12.5 million.

710
00:41:16,375 --> 00:41:18,709
We need some
spreading around money, Data.

711
00:41:18,750 --> 00:41:19,792
Sir?

712
00:41:19,834 --> 00:41:22,041
Bet it all.
Here you go.

713
00:41:22,083 --> 00:41:24,125
A little something
for you, Ziggy.

714
00:41:24,166 --> 00:41:26,667
