00:41:26,709 --> 00:41:29,250
Run this outside and give it
to the parking lot attendants.

716
00:41:29,291 --> 00:41:31,166
You're very kind, sir.

717
00:41:31,208 --> 00:41:33,375
Here you go, Vanessa.
A little something for you, too.

718
00:41:33,417 --> 00:41:34,834
Thank you.

719
00:41:34,875 --> 00:41:37,875
When the train comes in,
everybody rides.

720
00:41:37,917 --> 00:41:40,500
Yeah, and I'm getting
off at this station.

721
00:41:40,542 --> 00:41:43,917
After 18 passes,
air gets a little too thin

722
00:41:43,959 --> 00:41:45,709
