a prudent choice, sir.

726
00:41:51,333 --> 00:41:54,750
Hey, that's what
horse racing's about.

727
00:41:54,792 --> 00:41:56,125
Roll 'em, boy.

728
00:42:10,375 --> 00:42:11,792
CROUPIER:
Seven. Seven a winner.

729
00:42:11,834 --> 00:42:13,375
Whoo!

730
00:42:15,041 --> 00:42:16,834
The man has the touch.

731
00:42:18,917 --> 00:42:21,875
