747
00:42:59,166 --> 00:43:02,750
I like you fellas.
You got style.

748
00:43:02,792 --> 00:43:04,583
Let me buy
you guys a drink.

749
00:43:04,625 --> 00:43:06,333
Just enjoy the game.

750
00:43:06,375 --> 00:43:08,166
Don't let 'em change
the dice on you.

751
00:43:08,208 --> 00:43:10,208
TEXAS:
You got it.

752
00:43:14,250 --> 00:43:15,417
Phew.

